---
layout: base.njk
title: Contact | Levi Huff
description: Get in touch with Levi Huff for IT infrastructure, systems administration, and IT operations opportunities.
---

<div class="bg-surface-1 text-fg-1">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-site mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:gap-8">
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <p class="font-jb text-mono-xs tracking-[0.04em] uppercase text-amber" aria-hidden="true">&#9658; CONTACT</p>
          <h1 class="font-syne text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-fg-1 mt-3">Get in touch.</h1>
          <p class="font-plex text-lg text-fg-2 leading-relaxed mt-4 max-w-prose">I'm open to full-time positions and collaborative opportunities. Feel free to reach out if you'd like to discuss potential opportunities or have questions about my work.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 sm:mt-0 flex-shrink-0">
          <img
            src="/images/profile.jpg"
            alt="Levi Huff"
            class="w-28 h-28 sm:w-32 sm:h-32 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-hair-1"
            width="800"
            height="800"
            loading="eager">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">

        {# Contact info card #}
        <div class="bg-surface-2 border border-hair-1 rounded-d-lg p-6 md:p-8">
          <p class="font-jb text-mono-xs tracking-[0.04em] uppercase text-amber">EMAIL</p>
          <h2 class="font-syne text-xl font-semibold text-fg-1 mt-2">Direct contact</h2>
          <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" class="font-plex text-base text-amber hover:text-amber-hi transition-colors duration-[120ms] mt-3 block focus-visible:outline-[3px] focus-visible:outline-amber focus-visible:outline-offset-2">{{ site.email }}</a>

          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-3">
            <a href="{{ site.social.github }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-jb text-sm text-fg-2 hover:text-amber transition-colors duration-[120ms] focus-visible:outline-[3px] focus-visible:outline-amber focus-visible:outline-offset-2">GitHub &rarr;<span class="sr-only"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>
            <a href="{{ site.social.linkedin }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-jb text-sm text-fg-2 hover:text-amber transition-colors duration-[120ms] focus-visible:outline-[3px] focus-visible:outline-amber focus-visible:outline-offset-2">LinkedIn &rarr;<span class="sr-only"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>
            {% if site.social.handshake %}
            <a href="{{ site.social.handshake }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-jb text-sm text-fg-2 hover:text-amber transition-colors duration-[120ms] focus-visible:outline-[3px] focus-visible:outline-amber focus-visible:outline-offset-2">Handshake &rarr;<span class="sr-only"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </div>

        {# Looking for card #}
        <div class="bg-surface-2 border border-hair-1 rounded-d-lg p-6 md:p-8">
          <p class="font-jb text-mono-xs tracking-[0.04em] uppercase text-amber">LOOKING FOR</p>
          <h2 class="font-syne text-xl font-semibold text-fg-1 mt-2">What I am seeking</h2>
          <p class="font-plex text-sm text-fg-2 leading-relaxed mt-3">I am currently seeking full-time roles in IT infrastructure, systems administration, or IT operations.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
            <li class="font-plex text-sm text-fg-2">IT infrastructure and operations</li>
            <li class="font-plex text-sm text-fg-2">Systems administration and endpoint management</li>
            <li class="font-plex text-sm text-fg-2">Imaging, deployment, and provisioning</li>
            <li class="font-plex text-sm text-fg-2">Process improvement and automation</li>
            <li class="font-plex text-sm text-fg-2">Software and application development</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="font-jb text-mono-xs tracking-[0.04em] uppercase text-fg-3 mt-6">Availability: <span class="normal-case font-plex text-sm text-fg-2 tracking-normal">Available for full-time positions. Graduating {{ site.graduationDate }} from the University of Cincinnati.</span></p>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</div>
